                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-1366" type="given" value="ADAM"></interp>ADAM SPAREY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 36.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
